    public class SequenceSelection.SequenceIndex.SelectionWrongForDocumentsException
extends SequenceSelectionWithDocuments.SelectedDocumentsModifiedException
    Thrown to indicate that an attempt was made to resolve this SequenceSelection on some List<AnnotatedPluginDocument>, but that the documents were not valid for this selection.
    Since:
